    "text": "<div>Part 72:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F2:\t[2023/05/16 17:47:45 GMT+0000] And <span id=\"node3_169333895196013249\" class=\"highlighted\">who's he talking to</span>?&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F3:\tSo <span id=\"node8_169333895196013249\" class=\"highlighted\">she's talking to this guy</span>.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F2:\tOkay, so <span id=\"node14_169333895196013249\" class=\"highlighted\">it's just a new person, a new company</span>?&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F3:\tYeah. <span id=\"node19_169333895196013249\" class=\"highlighted\"> This is the people who probably want to do the development shit</span>.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F2:\t<span id=\"node38_169350312359265831\" class=\"highlighted\">Yeah</span>.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F3:\tSo, 'Thank you for taking the time to speak with me with this morning, my husband and I have been so troubled what's happening at the bar\u2026'&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F2:\t<span id=\"node50_169350312359265831\" class=\"highlighted\">They're trying to scare him off</span>.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>F3:\tYeah.  'Running Old Scratch means so much to Nick, but these days I can't shake the feeling that something terrible is going to happen to him.  As you can imagine, he's been preoccupied recently, so he asked me to handle the sale directly.'&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F2:\tYeah.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>F3:\t<span id=\"node64_169333895196013249\" class=\"highlighted\">Liar, pants on fire</span>.\n\n\t'I hope you understand.'  And so here the guy says, ''No trouble at all, I will be happy to discuss the details, I think you'll find them quite reasonable.\u2019  She says, 'I'm glad that we were able to come to agreement, we need a few weeks to put our affairs in order, and then we should be ready to finalise, thank you your patience\u2026'&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>F2:\t[00:00:30]: Oh they're so like\u2026</div>",
